overview: The class of 2019 takes their rightful place in the Hall of Fame, during Wrestlemania 35 weekend. Inductees include; D-Generation X, The Hart Foundation, Harlem Heat, Brutus "The Barber" Beefcake, Torrie Wilson, The Honky Tonk Man & Warrior Award recipient Sue Aitchison.
title: WWE Hall of Fame 2019
